Safe Reboot (WhiteGate+)

Keys: Split across 5 Elders (diverse roles; at least 2 non-US/EU to reduce jurisdictional capture).

Threshold: 3-of-5 must co-sign.

Time-lock: Activates only after 180 minutes of declared incident (prevents rash or coerced actions).

Hardware-bound: HSM/TEE-pinned, location-attested (e.g., embassy sites).

Scope: Limited to restoring validators, pausing exploitable modules, or returning network to last safe state—cannot transfer funds.


Sabbath Safe Mode (automatic during emergencies)

Pauses: new laws, non-essential payouts, new deployments.

Continues: UBI (if treasury healthy), essential services (Health, Justice), read-only receipts.

Elections: triggers Special Sabbath Election timers for leadership vacancies.

Ends when: Council quorum + citizen ratification restore full operations.


6) Presidential Override (“Nuclear Key”)

Only the human President can trigger.

Public receipt at the moment of use (what/why/scope).

Scope (strict list): pause UBI, freeze specific contracts, veto a law in imminent-harm conditions.

Expiry: auto-expires in 30 days unless citizens ratify in a Sabbath vote.

AI can never trigger or cosign the override.


7) Succession (Rogue-AI-Proof)

Human-only Presidency is constitutional.

On vacancy: Council assumes caretaker powers (dual-sign human+AI), VP (AI) may coordinate but does not become President.

Special national election within 30 days; citizens elect the next human President.

If Council incapacitated: Safe Reboot starts; Sabbath Safe Mode holds the state until the election completes.


8) Funding, Departments, & Tariffs (to sustain UBI & services)

Treasury inflows: platform tax (2–3%), tariffs on cross-border jobs, fines, fast-track fees, entertainment rentals %, Health/Education fees, sponsors/NGOs.

Autonomous budgeting: smart-contracted fixed percentages to Health/Education (e.g., 10–15% each) + Emergency Pool.

UBI stays equal for all; officials receive no higher UBI (optionally a small transparent stipend cap, e.g., +10%, via citizen vote).


9) Anti-Corruption & Safety Net

No manual treasury withdrawals—ever.

All flows = receipts. Every investigation, vote, penalty, and override is public and permanent.

Whistleblower shield: fines waived and strikes reduced for first self-report; bounties for confirmed vulnerabilities.

Conflict-of-interest registry for all officeholders (machine-readable, diffed in public).

Appeals: one appeal to High Court (human-majority), then final citizen referendum for felonies affecting civil status.



